        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 26 at 7:46PM CDT until June 26 at 8:30PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 746 PM CDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from 5 miles northeast of Romero to near Nara Visa, moving
southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Romero.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
